[
    {
        "source_sentence": "增壹阿含經卷第二",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東晉罽賓三藏瞿曇僧伽提婆譯",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "廣演品第三",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（一）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；已修行一法，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念佛。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告諸比丘：「云何修行念佛，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃？」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘白世尊曰：「諸法之本，如來所說。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願世尊為諸比丘說此妙義，諸比丘從如來聞已，便當受持。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之，吾當為汝廣分別之。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "答曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念佛。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀如來形，未曾離目；已不離目，便念如來功德：如來體者，金剛所成，十力具足，四無所畏，在眾勇健。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來顏貌，端正無雙，視之無厭；戒德成就，猶如金剛，而不可毀，清淨無瑕，亦如琉璃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來三昧，未始有減，已息永寂，而無他念；憍慢強梁，諸情憺怕，欲意、恚想、愚惑之心、猶豫網結，皆悉除盡。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來慧身，智無崖底，無所罣礙。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來身者，解脫成就，諸趣已盡，無復生分，言我當更墮於生死。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554a29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來身者，度知見城，知他人根，應度不度，此死生彼，周旋往來生死之際，有解脫者，無解脫者，皆具知之。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是謂修行念佛，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離佛念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b09_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（二）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；修行、廣布一法已，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念法。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告諸比丘：「云何修行念法，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃？」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘白世尊曰：「諸法之本，如來所說。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願世尊為諸比丘說此妙義，諸比丘從如來聞已，便當受持。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之，吾當為汝廣分別說。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "對曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b23_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告之曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念法。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "除諸欲愛，無有塵勞，渴愛之心，永不復興。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫正法者，於欲至無欲，離諸結縛、諸蓋之病。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此法猶如眾香之氣，無有瑕疵亂想之念。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是謂，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "修行念法者，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554b29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c03_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離法念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c03_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c04_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c04_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c05_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（三）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；修行一法已，便有名譽，成大功德，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念僧。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告諸比丘：「云何修行念僧，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃？」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘白世尊曰：「諸法之本，如來所說。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願世尊為諸比丘說此妙義，諸比丘從如來聞已，便當受持。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之，吾當為汝廣分別說。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "對曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念眾。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來聖眾，善業成就，質直順義，無有邪業，上下和穆，法法成就。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來聖眾，戒成就，三昧成就，智慧成就，解脫成就，度知見成就。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聖眾者，所謂四雙八輩，是謂如來聖眾，應當恭敬，承事禮順。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以然者，是世福田故。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於此眾中，皆同一器，亦以自度，復度他人至三乘道，如此之業名曰聖眾。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是謂，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若念僧者，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0554c28_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a01_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離僧念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a01_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a02_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a03_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a03_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（四）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；修行一法已，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念戒。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告諸比丘：「云何修行念戒，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃？」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘白世尊曰：「諸法之本，如來所說。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願世尊為諸比丘說此妙義，諸比丘從如來聞已，便當受持。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之，吾當為汝廣分別說。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘對曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念戒。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂戒者，息諸惡故。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "戒能成道，令人歡喜，戒纓絡身，現眾好故。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫禁戒者，猶吉祥瓶，所願便剋，諸道品法，皆由戒成。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行禁戒者，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離戒念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（五）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；修行一法已，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念施。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告諸比丘：「云何修行念施，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃？」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘白世尊曰：「諸法之本，如來所說。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願世尊為諸比丘說此妙義，諸比丘從如來聞已，便當受持。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之，吾當為汝廣分別說。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘對曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念施。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今所施，施中之上，永無悔心，無返報想，快得善利。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人罵我，我終不報；設人害我，手捲相加，刀杖相向，瓦石相擲，當起慈心，不興瞋恚。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我所施者，施意不絕。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是謂，比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名曰大施，便成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離施念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（六）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；修行一法已，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露法，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555b29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念天。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
