        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之，吾當為汝廣分別說。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘對曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念天。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身、口、意淨，不造穢行，行戒成身；身放光明，無所不照，成彼天身；善果報，成彼天身；眾行具足，乃成天身。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名曰念天，便得具足，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離天念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0555c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
