    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘對曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念休息。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂休息者，心意想息，志性詳諦，亦無卒暴，恒專一心，意樂閑居，常求方便，入三昧定。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常念不貪，勝光上達。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名曰念休息，便得具足，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離休息念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
