        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念安般。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556a28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂安般者。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若息長時，亦當觀知我今息長；若復息短，亦當觀知我今息短；若息極冷，亦當觀知我今息冷；若復息熱，亦當觀知我今息熱。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具觀身體，從頭至足皆當觀知。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b04_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復息有長短，亦當觀息有長有短，用心持身，知息長短，皆悉知之，尋息出入，分別曉了。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若心持身知息長短，亦復知之，數息長短，分別曉了。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名曰念安般，便得具足，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b11_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離安般念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b12_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b13_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b13_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b13_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（九）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；修行一法已，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為道，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念身。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告諸比丘：「云何修行念身，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃？」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘白世尊曰：「諸法之本，如來所宣。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願世尊為諸比丘說此妙法，諸比丘從如來聞法已，便當受持。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之，吾當為汝廣分別說。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘對曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念身。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念身者，髮、毛、爪、齒、皮、肉、筋、骨、膽、肝、肺、心、脾、腎、大腸、小腸、白[月*直]、膀胱、屎、尿、百葉、滄、蕩、脾、泡、溺、淚、唾、涕、膿、血、肪脂、[泳永+羡]、髑髏、腦。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者是身為？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "地種是也？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "水種是也？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "火種是耶？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "風種是也？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為父種、母種所造耶？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從何處來？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為誰所造？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眼、耳、鼻、口、身、心，此終當生何處？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名曰念身，便得具足，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c07_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c10_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離身念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c10_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c11_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c11_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（一〇）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；修行一法已，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念死。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告諸比丘：「云何修行念死，便有名譽，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃？」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘白世尊曰：「諸法之本，如來所宣。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願世尊為諸比丘說此妙法，諸比丘從如來聞法已，便當受持。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之，吾當為汝廣分別說。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘對曰：「如是。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸比丘前受教已。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：「若有比丘正身正意，結跏趺坐，繫念在前，無有他想，專精念死。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂死者，此沒生彼，往來諸趣，命逝不停，諸根散壞，如腐敗木，命根斷絕，宗族分離，無形無響，亦無相貌。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0556c28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0557a01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名曰念死，便得具足，成大果報，諸善普至，得甘露味，至無為處，便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0557a01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0557a04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "常當思惟，不離死念，便當獲此諸善功德。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0557a04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0557a05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0557a06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0557a06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　佛、法及聖眾，　　乃至竟死念，　雖與上同名，　　其義各別異。",
        "from": "T02n0125_002:0557a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "增壹阿含經卷第二",
